		<div id="comment_body_64136453">Im not taking about what goes on inside the defense committee. Yeah, the reality is understood by  most of the academic and research  community. Im talking about the larger society where occasionally some academic pisses off someone with enough motivation to feed their work through Turnitin and post the results on X. That thesis by Ackerman wife? 330 pages with just a handful of problematic sentences? We both know that would prolly get marked as 1 or 2 percent problematic which is pretty damn good.</div>
	</div>

